data.description: Welcome to 1335 Romero Dr. This beautiful 2 story home in the Villa Verde subdivision in heart of Pearland has 4 bedrooms, a media/game room, office/flex room, 3.5 bath and 3 car garage. The spacious living room has an open floor plan with high ceilings that is perfect for gatherings and entertaining. Primary suite is located on first floor and has a sitting area, ensuite with double vanity, soaking tub, stand up shower and spacious walk in closet. The kitchen has granite countertops, a farmhouse sink and a plenty of room at the breakfast bar. The backyard is fully fenced with a patio and no back neighbors for additional privacy. Home has never flooded!   Schedule your private tour today.
